lore_integration: 9 -- The world is doing real work. Release classes, delay markers, casualty models, family injunctions, command records, denial edits, Exit streams, and Witness concurrence all drive the chapter's conflict. This could not be moved to a generic council chamber without losing its engine.
engagement: 8 -- The chapter is highly engaging because every argument wounds a different claim to the dead. The strongest surprise is Ruth's question to Mara about whether she would be the trained reviewer. Tension comes less from plot mechanics than from irreconcilable moral claims, which is right for this chapter.
